                <p>
                    It-turk⌈
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>kaiyāṟai Eḻunt-aruḷavi
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>ttān vaikā-v-uṭaiy
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ān ce<choice><orig>nn</orig><reg>ṉṉ</reg></choice>i nalla nāka⌈
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>vēḷāṉ                    
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
