                    Prosperity! Fortune!
                </p>
                
                <p n="1-5">
                    He who had this Turkkaiyār<note>Sanskrit Durgā.</note> installed is Vaikāvuṭaiyāṉ Ceṉṉi Nalla Nākavēḷāṉ
                </p>
                
